Adjustments to work with vertex smearing.

For Overlay and DDCaloDigi, change the start of the time window to -10ns.
Otherwise, if vertex smearing is enabled (with a width of 1.9ns), then
the existing defaults (of -0.25 and -1 ns, respectively) will exclude
a large fraction of hits.
